      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大学一年生　春",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Spring‚ 1st year of college",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "謝罪する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 79.9333251756
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "連絡出来なくて、ごめん",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm sorry for not contacting you.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 79.9333251756,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei005.m4a",
              "text": "いいよ、もう気にしてないから\n{user}君も\n忙しかったんだもんね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's okay‚ I don't mind anymore. You\nwere busy too‚ {user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 83.0666585089,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "久しぶりに会ったんだしさ\n今度また一緒に遊ばないか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's been a while since we last met‚\nwant to hang out sometime?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 90.7999882819,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 94.7002823951
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei006.m4a",
              "text": "あー……うん、そうだね\n今はちょっと忙しくて……君の時間が\nある時にメッセージを送って欲しいな",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ah… um‚ okay. I'm a little busy\nright now… Send me a message when\nyou have time.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 95.3999877733,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 19666.673807099996
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 107.7999842129
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei007.m4a",
              "text": "それじゃあ、お友達が呼んでるから\n芽衣はそろそろ行くね！\nまたね、{user}君！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Well‚ my friends are calling me‚ so\nMei should get going! See you‚\n{user}-kun!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 107.7999842129,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "（あれから何度か芽衣にメッセージを送ろう\nと思ったが、返信が来ないかもしれないと\n考えると送信ボタンは押せなかった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(After that‚ I tried to message Mei\nseveral times‚ but I couldn't press\nthe send button because I was\nafraid she wouldn't reply.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 119.0666539312,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "告白する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "なぁ……俺がまだお前のことを\n好きだって言ったら、どうする？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hey… what would you do if I told you\nI still liked you?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 132.3666554571,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 138.0999887904
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei008.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣、お前って言われるのやだな\nちゃんと芽衣って名前で呼んで欲しい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei doesn't like being called \"hey\".\nPlease call me by my name‚ \"Mei\".",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 138.0999887904,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "ご、ごめん……\n俺がまだ芽衣のことを好きだとしたら……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "S-sorry… If I still liked you‚ Mei…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 146.6666554571,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 151.0613267065
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei009.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣も好きだよ\n{user}君は大事な友達だもん\n友達として、大好きだよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I like you too. You're a precious\nfriend‚ {user}-kun. I really\nlike you‚ as a friend.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 151.7666554571,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 162.3666503708
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "そうか……そう、だよな\nごめん、変なこと言って\n気にしないでくれ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I see… R-right. Sorry‚ I said\nsomething weird.\nDon't worry about\nit.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 162.3666503708,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei010.m4a",
              "text": "それじゃ、芽衣は帰り道こっちだから\nバイバイ、{user}君",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Well then‚ I'm going this way. Bye‚\n{user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 171.2999959111,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 9012.624962999978
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "ああ、またな……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yeah‚ see you…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 177.9666544397,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "（あれから何度か芽衣にメッセージを\n送ったが返信が返ってくることも\n既読が付くこともなかった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(After that‚ I sent Mei several\nmessages‚ but she never replied. And\nthe messages were never marked as\nread.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 184.2333241581,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.5999999166
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lovehroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lovehroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.5999999166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（地元へと戻った俺は部活と勉強に\n忙殺され、気づけば芽衣への\n連絡を怠っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After returning to my hometown‚ I\nwas so busy with club activities and\nstudies that I neglected to contact\nMei.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666665833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣から連絡はきていたが\n返信を後回しにする内に\n気づけば高校生活が終わっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mei had contacted me‚ but I kept\nputting off replying‚ and before I\nknew it‚ high school was over.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0333331228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.4999991735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（そして大学へと進学した俺は\nサークルの新歓に参加した帰り道\n見知った人物に遭遇した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And after entering university‚ I\nwas on my way back from a club\norientation when I ran into a\nfamiliar face.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3999974371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7833.3358961999975
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 26.5205645681
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.1
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 28.8666658839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、もしかして{user}君？\nこんなところで会うなんてびっくりだ～\n全然変わってないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ could it be… {user}-kun?\nIt's so surprising to see you here~!\nYou haven't changed at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8666658839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……？　芽衣……？\nまさかこっちに出て来てたなんて……\nそっちの方が驚きだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? Mei…? I can't believe you came\nall the way here… I'm more\nsurprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0999976915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.0666653754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君が過ごしてる場所が\nどんな所なのかずっと気になってたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always been curious about the\nplace where {user}-kun lives~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0666653754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "だから一生懸命勉強して\nこっちの大学に進学したんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I studied really hard and got\ninto this university!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5666671556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.6999976915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか\n連絡くらいくれれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see. You could have at least\ncontacted me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6999976915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、何回かしたけどね\nところで{user}君は\n今までどうしていたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I did a few times. By the way‚\nwhat have you been up to‚\n{user}-kun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4999918422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、ずっと部活と勉強をしてたよ\nそれで、忙しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been busy with club activities\nand studying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0666585089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.9333251756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
